      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "If an exception is thrown, the streams would not be closed until they&#39;re garbage collected, and <a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/515975/closing-streams-in-java#comment5185168_515981\">that&#39;s not good</a>. Consider closing them in <code>finally</code>."
