    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Kotlin extension for it</p>\n\n<pre><code>fun File.copyTo(file: File) {\n    inputStream().use { input -&gt;\n        file.outputStream().use { output -&gt;\n            input.copyTo(output)\n        }\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
