    "body" : "<p>Much simpler now with Kotlin:</p>\n\n<pre><code> File(\"originalFileDir\", \"originalFile.name\")\n            .copyTo(File(\"newFileDir\", \"newFile.name\"), true)\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><code>true</code>or<code>false</code> is for overwriting the destination file</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://kotlinlang.org/api/latest/jvm/stdlib/kotlin.io/java.io.-file/copy-to.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">https://kotlinlang.org/api/latest/jvm/stdlib/kotlin.io/java.io.-file/copy-to.html</a></p>\n"
